2 - After run the jdk it will save C:\Program Files\Java this location

3 - set the path same as in user veribles JAVA_HOME -- C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.8.0_181
                             system veribles path --- C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.8.0_181\bin
                             
